    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/b58be01b8b431cf88a7093b965977b00.avif?t=1770322536\" width=1138 height=640 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of the same old shooters? We hear you. In Uniqkiller, you create heroes with distinct appearances, skills, and styles for PvP battles in urban environments! The controls are so simple, that even your grandma could play. But don’t get us wrong – it’s fast, intense, and packed with endless possibilities. Play on PC or mobile, build your own path, and watch your &quot;Seekers&quot; shine and reach the spotlights.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/3b9a50726d06ce2a857e195fdd7a2fdc.avif?t=1770322536\" width=750 height=161 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead of settling for pre-made characters that need to be unlocked, you customize your operator by combining body type and parts, outfits, combat classes, skills and weapons to create a unique hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shape your gameplay and progression path. In Uniqkiller, your choices in creating and improving characters directly impact how you play and grow!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/d02974ee54c3be6fed79dd40a8e2c557.poster.avif?t=1770322536\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/d02974ee54c3be6fed79dd40a8e2c557.webm?t=1770322536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/b6872902d66b0127f56c6b082615ac40.avif?t=1770322536\" width=750 height=161 /></span>With an auto-shooting system and simple, intuitive controls, Uniqkiller is easy to pick up and play. But the depth of customization for your operators, the variety of game modes, the top-down perspective, and tactical combat mechanics push the limits of strategic thinking — challenging players to truly stand out, whether you’re a rookie or a pro.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/04b4f0758009d4db7aaf485ab0968712.poster.avif?t=1770322536\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/04b4f0758009d4db7aaf485ab0968712.webm?t=1770322536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/04b4f0758009d4db7aaf485ab0968712.mp4?t=1770322536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/d9e77178cf9996da8d067b77dd41fb51.avif?t=1770322536\" width=750 height=161 /></span>Uniqkiller is the first-ever Urban Shooter — where battles unfold across realistic cityscapes inspired by real-world locations. Gritty, modern, and unapologetically urban — no fantasy worlds here, just pure street attitude.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/1682dea1007a58182a55506cf13ee985.poster.avif?t=1770322536\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/1682dea1007a58182a55506cf13ee985.webm?t=1770322536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/1682dea1007a58182a55506cf13ee985.mp4?t=1770322536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/d7aa44082e9d76f15fabca8c80a41e1c.avif?t=1770322536\" width=750 height=161 /></span>Uniqkiller isn’t just about playing. It’s about being seen and making an impact. <strong>You start as a “Seeker”.</strong> The more you stand out in the game, the closer you get to becoming a “Uniqk” — legendary players who’ve left their mark so deeply that they’ve been immortalized as collectible plushies, exclusive skins, in-game lore, and real-world rewards delivered right to your door.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/6e85f7e3dd3a60e1528190a8376c4097.avif?t=1770322536\" width=681 height=257 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/1046de84f8e9c54ba5ebc2417c62f52e.avif?t=1770322536\" width=776 height=156 /></span>UniqKiller is a free to play cross platform and crossplay (PC and mobile), meaning that you can play whenever you are. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/56ecd455ab27204de8e56104805aba43.avif?t=1770322536\" width=776 height=156 /></span>Play with or against your friends. Form alliances or start wars. It’s all about standing out — solo or with your squad. Uniqkiller gives you all the tools to make your mark. To connect with other players and share your experience, join our Discord community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/a03bfa130b01aa7cc302feff91ff136c.poster.avif?t=1770322536\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099330/extras/a03bfa130b01aa7cc302feff91ff136c.webm?t=1770322536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
